<topic id="filters-outliner">
  <title>Outline Specific Actions</title><prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords><indexterm>XML Outline View<indexterm>outliner filters</indexterm></indexterm></keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The following actions are available in the <ph product="editor author"
          ><uicontrol>Settings</uicontrol> menu of the Outline view</ph><ph
        product="editorEclipse authorEclipse"><uicontrol>View menu</uicontrol> of the Outline
        view</ph>:<ul>
        <li><uicontrol>Filter returns exact matches</uicontrol> - the text filter of the
            <uicontrol>Outline</uicontrol> view returns only exact matches.</li>
        <li id="outline-flat-presentation-mode"><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_flat_presentation"
          /></li>
        <li><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_show_comments"
          /></li>
        <li><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/show_element_name"
          /></li>
        <li><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/comments_sjow_text"
          /></li>
        <li><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_show_attributes"
          /></li>
        <li id="outline-configure-displayed-attrs"><ph
            conref="relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view.dita#relax-ng-schema-diagram-outline-view/outline_configure_attributes"
          /></li>
      </ul></p>
    <p id="outliner-filter-box">The upper part of the view contains a filter box which allows you to
      focus on the relevant components. Type a text fragment in the filter box and only the
      components that match it are presented. For advanced usage you can use wildcard characters (*,
      ?) and separate multiple patterns with commas.</p>
  </body>
